---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>üèùÔ∏è Hello, Traveller!</h1>
			<p>
				Welcome to <a href="https://explore-azerbaijan.vercel.app/">ExploreAzerbaijan	</a>, your ultimate guide to experiencing the beauty and culture of Azerbaijan! 
				Whether you're planning your first visit or you're a seasoned traveler to this enchanting land, 
				we're here to provide you with all the information, tips, and inspiration you need to make your journey unforgettable.
			</p>
			<p>
				At ExploreAzerbaijan, we're passionate about showcasing the rich tapestry of experiences that Azerbaijan has to offer. 
				From the bustling streets of Baku to the serene landscapes of the Caucasus Mountains, each corner of this diverse country 
				has its own story to tell.
			</p>
			<p>Through our blog, we aim to be your trusted companion as you explore Azerbaijan. 
				From practical travel advice and insider tips to in-depth cultural insights and off-the-beaten-path recommendations, 
				we're dedicated to helping you make the most of your time in this remarkable destination.</p>

			
